WEBVTT

00:02:58.668 --> 00:03:00.041
Morali biste da se zamotate

00:03:00.041 --> 00:03:01.921
kako biste održali temperaturu tela

00:03:01.921 --> 00:03:03.590
iznad 35 stepeni Celzijusa,

00:03:03.590 --> 00:03:06.230
ili biste počeli snažno da drhtite

00:03:06.230 --> 00:03:08.169
i postepeno postajete mentalno zbunjeni

00:03:08.169 --> 00:03:09.663
i na kraju biste pali s neba

00:03:09.663 --> 00:03:11.309
zbog gubitka kontrole mišića

00:03:11.309 --> 00:03:13.379
od hipotermije!

00:03:14.272 --> 00:03:16.221
Zakon idealnog gasa navodi

00:03:16.221 --> 00:03:17.927
da kako se smanjuje pritisak,

00:03:17.927 --> 00:03:19.756
tako raste zapremina gasa.

00:03:19.756 --> 00:03:21.756
Kada biste leteli pravo previše brzo,

00:03:21.756 --> 00:03:24.620
inertni gas u vašem telu
bi se naglo raširio

00:03:24.620 --> 00:03:27.457
kao što se gazirano piće zapeni
kada ga protresete.

00:03:27.457 --> 00:03:30.032
Ova pojava se zove aeroembolizam,